bench = []

[[bin]]
bench = true
doc = true
doctest = true
edition = "2018"
harness = true
name = "sensor-pollster"
path = "src/main.rs"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []
test = true

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.38"
async-stream = "0.3.0"
btleplug = "0.7.1"
chrono = "0.4.19"
clap = "2.33.3"
env_logger = "0.8.3"
eui48 = "0.4.6"
futures = "0.3.13"
indoc = "1.0.3"
log = "0.4.14"
rand = "0.8.3"
serde = "1.0.124"
serde_with = "1.6.4"
serde_yaml = "0.8.17"
thiserror = "1.0.24"
tokio-stream = "0.1.4"
uuid = "0.8.0"

[dependencies.ctrlc]
features = ["termination"]
optional = false
version = "3.1.8"

[dependencies.tokio]
features = ["sync", "time", "macros", "rt", "rt-multi-thread"]
optional = false
version = "1.3.0"

[dependencies.tokio-postgres]
features = ["with-chrono-0_4", "with-eui48-0_4"]
optional = false
version = "0.7.0"

[package]
authors = ["Shuhao <johnmave126@gmail.com.>"]
autobenches = true
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
categories = []
description = "Monitor temperature from HM-11 sensors"
edition = "2018"
keywords = ["bluetooth", "ble"]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
name = "sensor-pollster"
publish = true
version = "0.1.1"
